(1, 3, 'Company Registration in Jaipur', 'company-registration-in-jaipur', 'Company Registration refers to the process of forming and creating a business entity in a legal way.', '<p>Company Registration refers to the process of forming and creating a business entity in a legal way.</p>', '1760705722_design-accounting-education-financial-literacy-improve-economic-growth_4968-1462.jpg', 0, '2025-09-18 07:34:55', '2025-11-08 05:28:31'),
(2, 2, 'Tax Saving Tips for Freelancers in India: A CA’s Expert Advice', 'tax-saving-tips-for-freelancers-in-india-a-cas-expert-advice', 'Freelancers in India know taxes are not as simple as they sound. Income comes from different sources, payments can be', '<p>Freelancers in India know taxes are not as simple as they sound. Income comes from different sources, payments can be</p>', '1760705713_design-accounting-education-financial-literacy-improve-economic-growth_4968-1462.jpg', 1, '2025-09-19 00:33:34', '2025-11-08 04:28:22'),
(3, 1, 'singage board', 'singage-board', 'Introduction When GST was introduced in 2017', '<p>Introduction When GST was introduced in 2017, it promised to be a &ldquo;one nation, one tax&rdquo; solution to the citizens</p>', '1762518228_blog1.webp', 1, '2025-09-19 00:34:14', '2025-11-07 06:53:48'),
(4, 4, 'roadside-board', 'roadside-board', 'Innovate Create Inspire your brand to life in', '<p>Many businesses overlook the importance of legal strategies and protections. But the increasing complexity of laws makes it clear&mdash;every company needs a dedicated approach to legal safety. Not having strong legal safeguards can put your company at risk of fines, lawsuits, or reputation damage. It&rsquo;s smarter to act now, and a well-planned legal strategy can save you serious trouble later. This article explores why organizations must focus on legal benefits and risk mitigation through a clear role of<strong>&nbsp;</strong></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>', '1760705747_design-accounting-education-financial-literacy-improve-economic-growth_4968-1462.jpg', 1, '2025-10-17 05:57:19', '2025-11-08 04:28:20'),
(5, 3, 'digi grow singages', 'digi-grow-singages', 'Lorem Ipsum is simply dummy text of the printing and typesetting industry.', '<p>Contrary to popular belief, Lorem Ipsum is not simply random text. It has roots in a piece of classical Latin literature from 45 BC, making it over 2000 years old. Richard McClintock, a Latin professor at Hampden-Sydney College in Virginia, looked up one of the more obscure Latin words, consectetur, from a Lorem Ipsum passage, and going through the cites of the word in classical literature, discovered the undoubtable source. Lorem Ipsum comes from sections 1.10.32 and 1.10.33 of \"de Finibus Bonorum et Malorum\" (The Extremes of Good and Evil) by Cicero, written in 45 BC. This book is a treatise on the theory of ethics, very popular during the Renaissance. The first line of Lorem Ipsum, \"Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet..\", comes from a line in section 1.10.32.</p>\r\n<p>The standard chunk of Lorem Ipsum used since the 1500s is reproduced below for those interested. Sections 1.10.32 and 1.10.33 from \"de Finibus Bonorum et Malorum\" by Cicero are also reproduced in their exact original form, accompanied by E</p>', '1762518546.webp', 1, '2025-11-07 06:59:14', '2025-11-07 06:59:36');

